The paper deals with the use of machine learning techniques for the identification of bird species based on their songs. This falls under the domain of signal processing and machine learning, which are covered by the sub-categories cs.SD, cs.AI, cs.LG, and cs.NE. Additionally, the paper also mentions the use of clustering-based approaches, which falls under the domain of unsupervised learning and could be covered by the sub-category cs.CL.
